Subject: [PATCH] drm/me/gsc: mei interrupt top half should be in irq disabled context
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 17445af7dcc7d645b6fb8951fd10c8b72cc7f23f
